\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile9.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F266F88405459CB17190DE0\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; FLOAT: none; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile26.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F236EE5405459CB19193229\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">표고버섯에는 천연 감미료인 구아닐산이 있으니 참나물표고초무침을 해서 먹으면 입에 들러붙는 맛이 율무밥과 잘 어울릴 것 이다. 10월과 11월 가을에 수확하는 율무와 표고버섯을 잘 어울리는 한 쌍의 밥상이다. 술로 몸에 열이 찬 사람들은 율무밥과 표고버섯 반찬의 밥상을 시도해보라.</span></p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <br> \n <br> \n <div style=\"text-align:center\"> \n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;width:50%;min-width:300px;margin:0 -1px;text-align:center\"> \n   <script name=\"cpt_script\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://leaderstime.co.kr/nicead/ad_script_new.asp?tid=m90abcd12127\"></script> \n  </div> \n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;width:50%;min-width:300px;margin:0 -1px;text-align:center\"> \n   <script name=\"cpt_script\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://leaderstime.co.kr/nicead/ad_script_new.asp?tid=i01abcd12125\"></script> \n  </div> \n </div> \n <br> \n <br> \n</div>","images":["http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile29.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2218814F5459B29D153417","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2117E03E5459BB332892B9","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile7.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2529123E5459BB350D9AA7","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F26136C3E5459BB3731BDCB","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile28.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2721CF3E5459BB39187DDB","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile7.uf.ti